BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 727.00 Td (Initial y it was assumed that adult attachment styles were primarily a product of your upbringing. Thus, it) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 713.25 Td (was hypothesized that your current attachment style is determined by the way in which you were cared) Tj ET
