BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 672.00 Td (style; and if they were distant, rigid, and unresponsive, you should develop an avoidant attachment) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 658.25 Td (style. Today, however, we know that attachment styles in adulthood are influenced by a variety of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 644.50 Td (factors, one of which is the way our parents cared for us, but other factors also come into play,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 630.75 Td (including our genes and life experiences. For more, see chapter 7.) Tj ET
