BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 263.00 Td (setting, the intimate bonds formed by investing greatly in a particular individual would yield greater) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 249.25 Td (benefits for both the individual and his or her offspring \(hence, the secure attachment style\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 229.50 Td (True, in modern society, we are not hunted by predators as our ancestors were, but in evolutionary) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 215.75 Td (terms we’re only a fraction of a second away from the old scheme of things. Our emotional brain was) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 202.00 Td (handed down to us by Homo sapiens who lived in a completely different era, and it is their lifestyle and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 188.25 Td (the dangers they encountered that our emotions were designed to address. Our feelings and behaviors) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 174.50 Td (in relationships today are not very different from those of our early ancestors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 154.75 Td (PROTEST BEHAVIOR IN THE DIGITAL AGE) Tj ET
