BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 213.25 Td (style react more strongly to thoughts of loss and at the same time under-recruit regions normal y used) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 199.50 Td (to down-regulate negative emotions. This means that once your attachment system is activated, you wil) Tj ET
