BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 575.75 Td (for intimacy and togetherness the rest of the time. By being someone you’re not, you’re al owing) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 562.00 Td (another to be with you on his or her own terms and come and go as s/he pleases.) Tj ET
