BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 440.00 Td (A COACHING SESSION FOR THE ANXIOUS) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 420.25 Td (ATTACHMENT STYLE ON A DATE) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 400.50 Td (1. Acknowledge and accept your true relationship needs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 380.75 Td (Do we recommend that you do al the pursuing, fulfil your partner’s every wish, and cal incessantly?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 367.00 Td (Definitely not. We suggest a completely different approach. It stems from the understanding that you) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 353.25 Td (—given your anxious attachment style—have certain clear needs in a relationship. If those needs are not) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 339.50 Td (met, you cannot be truly happy. The key to finding a mate who can fulfil those needs is to first ful y) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 325.75 Td (acknowledge your need for intimacy, availability, and security in a relationship—and to believe that they) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 312.00 Td (are legitimate. They aren’t good or bad, they are simply your needs. Don’t let people make you feel) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 298.25 Td (guilty for acting “needy” or “dependent.” Don’t be ashamed of feeling incomplete when you’re not in a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 284.50 Td (relationship, or for wanting to be close to your partner and to depend on him.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 264.75 Td (Next, use this knowledge. Start assessing people you date on the basis of their ability to meet those) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 251.00 Td (needs. Instead of thinking how you can change yourself in order to please your partner, as so many) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 237.25 Td (relationship books advise, think: Can this person provide what I need in order to be happy?) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 217.50 Td (2. Recognize and rule out avoidant prospects early on.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 197.75 Td (The second step is to recognize and rule out people with an avoidant attachment style early on. This is) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 184.00 Td (where our questionnaire for deciphering the style of others comes in handy. But there are also other) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 170.25 Td (ways to tel whether you’ve met someone avoidant. Arthur Conan Doyle coined the term “smoking) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 156.50 Td (gun” in one of his Sherlock Holmes detective novels. A smoking gun has since become a reference for) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 142.75 Td (an object or a fact that serves as conclusive evidence of not just a crime but any type of undeniable) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 129.00 Td (proof. We like to cal any signal or message that is highly indicative of avoidance a smoking gun:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 115.25 Td (SMOKING GUNS THAT INDICATE YOU’RE) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 95.50 Td (DATING SOMEONE AVOIDANT) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 75.75 Td (• Sends mixed messages—about his/her feelings toward you or about his/her commitment to you.) Tj ET
