BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 81.00 Td (• Flirting with others—a hurtful way to introduce insecurity into the relationship.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 61.25 Td (• Not saying “I love you”—while implying that you do have feelings toward the other person.) Tj ET
