BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 644.50 Td (had endless patience to deal with her silences, moods, and scorn. Stil , Carole was adamant about her) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 630.75 Td (need to leave Bob. “It wil never work,” she said time and again. Final y, she broke up with him. Months) Tj ET
