BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 482.25 Td (THE TEXT MESSAGE THAT SAVED THE DAY) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 462.50 Td (When we interviewed Georgia and Henry for the book, they were constantly quarreling. According to) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 448.75 Td (Henry, nothing he ever did was good enough for Georgia, and he was always being judged and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 435.00 Td (criticized. Georgia, for her part, believed that the onus of the marriage was on her. She had to run after) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 421.25 Td (Henry to make even simple plans and was always the one to initiate everything—from buying a birthday) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 407.50 Td (present for his mother to deciding which apartment to rent. She felt very alone in the partnership. When) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 393.75 Td (we encouraged Georgia to start monitoring her working model, which was clearly anxious, she came up) Tj ET
