BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 378.25 Td (She doesn’t react defensively and resort to counterattacks. She doesn’t return tit for tat. She maintains) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 364.50 Td (focus on the problem at hand and responds to it and to it alone. This is not to say that Dan’s anger wil) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 350.75 Td (disappear; in fact, he most probably will remain irritated. But Shannon has managed to take the edge) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 337.00 Td (off his anger and avoid escalation. Her response shows that reacting securely to conflict is not rocket) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 323.25 Td (science; it doesn’t require amazing verbal or psychological skil s. It can often come down to simple but) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 309.50 Td (sincere apology.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 289.75 Td (Epilogue) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 270.00 Td (For us, the most important take-home message from this book is that relationships should not be left to) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 256.25 Td (chance. Relationships are one of the most rewarding of human experiences, above and beyond other) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 242.50 Td (gifts that life has to offer. In fact, one study found that 73 percent of over three hundred university) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 228.75 Td (student participants were wil ing to sacrifice the majority of their goals in life for a romantic relationship.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 215.00 Td (But despite the importance we assign to our most intimate bonds, most of us stil know very little about) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 201.25 Td (the science behind romantic relationships and al ow ourselves al too often to be guided by) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 187.50 Td (misconceptions and myths.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 167.75 Td (Even the two of us, having thoroughly studied the science behind adult attachment styles, occasional y) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 154.00 Td (find ourselves fal ing back into familiar patterns of thinking when we hear a certain love story or watch a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 140.25 Td (romantic movie that pushes al our old buttons. We recently saw a popular boy-meets-girl film that did) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 126.50 Td (just that. A young man fal s passionately in love with a beautiful and intel igent woman. He becomes) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 112.75 Td (consumed by the desire to spend the rest of his life with her.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 93.00 Td (She, on the other hand, is determined to stay free and unattached— and tel s him so from the start.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 79.25 Td (Throughout the story, she sends mixed messages; she flirts and strings him along, which al ows him to) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 65.50 Td (keep hoping for a happy ending. But in an atypical Hol ywood twist, she breaks his heart. He later) Tj ET
endstream
