BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 727.00 Td (Instead of recognizing that someone who blatantly disregards our emotions is not going to be a good) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 713.25 Td (partner, we accept this attitude. Again, we must constantly remind ourselves: In a true partnership, both) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 699.50 Td (partners view it as their responsibility to ensure the other’s emotional well-being.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 679.75 Td (Once we let go of these delusions, the movie, like many situations in life, takes on a very different) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 666.00 Td (meaning. The story line becomes predictable and loses much of its mystique. It’s no longer a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 652.25 Td (boy-meets-girl story, but an avoidant-meets-anxious one; he has a need for intimacy and she shies) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 638.50 Td (away from it. The writing was on the wal from the beginning, but the movie’s male hero couldn’t see it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 624.75 Td (That the woman he loved went on to marry someone else doesn’t change the fact that she was) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 611.00 Td (avoidant, and it predicts nothing about her happiness \(or her husband’s\) in the marriage. It’s very) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 597.25 Td (likely that she continued her behavior and distanced herself from the husband in many ways. For al we) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 583.50 Td (know, the hero became her phantom ex.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 563.75 Td (What we learned from watching the film is just how hard it is to let go of concepts we’ve believed in our) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 550.00 Td (entire lives—no matter how unhelpful they’ve been. But jettisoning these ideas is a necessary step;) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 536.25 Td (holding on to them can be highly destructive. They encourage us to compromise our self-esteem and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 522.50 Td (happiness by ignoring our most basic needs and trying to be someone we’re not.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 502.75 Td (We believe that every person deserves to experience the benefits of a secure bond. When our partner) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 489.00 Td (acts as our secure base and emotional anchor, we derive strength and encouragement to go out into) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 475.25 Td (the world and make the most of ourselves. He or she is there to help us become the best person we) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 461.50 Td (can be, as we are for them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 441.75 Td (Don’t Lose Sight of These Facts:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 422.00 Td (• Your attachment needs are legitimate.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 402.25 Td (• You shouldn’t feel bad for depending on the person you are closest to—it is part of your genetic) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 388.50 Td (makeup.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 368.75 Td (• A relationship, from an attachment perspective, should make you feel more self-confident and give) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 355.00 Td (you peace of mind. If it doesn’t, this is a wake-up cal !) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 335.25 Td (• And above al , remain true to your authentic self—playing games wil only distance you from your) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 321.50 Td (ultimate goal of finding true happiness, be it with your current partner or with someone else.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 301.75 Td (We hope you wil use the relationship wisdom distil ed in this book, from more than two decades of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 288.00 Td (research, to find happiness in your romantic connections and to soar in al aspects of your life. If you fol) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 274.25 Td (ow the attachment principles we have outlined, you wil be actively giving yourself the best shot at) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 260.50 Td (finding—and keeping—a deeply gratifying love, instead of leaving one of the most important aspects of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 246.75 Td (your life to chance!) Tj ET
